Plethico Seeks Approval to Reset Convertible Bond Maturity Term

-- B y   A n o o p   A g r a w a l
-- 
2011-10-17T06:08:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/plethico-seeks-approval-to-reset-convertible-bond-maturity-term.html
Plethico Pharmaceuticals Ltd. (PLEP) , an
Indian drugmaker, has sought approval from the central bank to
reset terms of the $75 million convertible bonds that are due in
October 2012, Chief Financial Officer Sanjay Pai said in a
telephone interview from Mumbai.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anoop Agrawal in Mumbai at 
